Actions.Title: How many times execute macro?
Actions.Prompt: Please enter the details for these variables.

Actions.Text:
use AppleScript version "2.4" -- Yosemite (10.10) or later
use scripting additions

on run
	tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine"
		set numberOfURLs to getvariable "Count"
	end tell
	
	tell application "Microsoft Excel"
		tell active workbook
			tell active sheet
				set urlList to string value of range ("$A$1:$A$" & numberOfURLs)
			end tell
		end tell
	end tell
	
	tell application "Safari"
		tell window 1
			repeat with oneURL in urlList
				--just in case we pick up some blank rows
				if (oneURL as string) â‰  "" then
					make new tab with properties {URL:(item 1 of oneURL)}
				end if
			end repeat
		end tell
	end tell
end run
